::Aerotaur::
       He charges around corners in the base locking on to Kup's signal.  He 
finally arrives in the room where the paralyzing gas had mostly dissipated 
into the air.  He continues to follow the signal to Kup's now paralyzed body. 
 He stops only for a moment to make sure Kup is still alive and begins 
surveying the room for Flicker.  He raises both of his arms to show that he 
meant no harm.  "Flicker, I think we need to have a little talk."

--part1_164.1e06e510.2bb4b942_boundary
